data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION! This spacious four bedroom, three and a half bathroom home in Miami Springs offers 2,290 square feet of living space on a 10,800 square feet lot. The home is secured with impact windows and doors for peace of mind and storm protection. Inside the home you’ll find a bright living room area with lots of natural light, an office/den space to compliment as a living/bonus room adjacent to the kitchen. This home features updated kitchen and bathrooms, dual rain shower, new flooring, smart appliances, a coffee station with a wine cooler, central AC, new water heater, and various other updates. The backyard boasts a refreshing pool, outdoor shower, also features a beautiful sitting area, nestled under a pergola, BBQ with a nearby firepit to complete your outdoor space. CALL L/A
